'''吴丹岛'''（{{lang-en|U Thant Island}}），官方稱為'''貝爾蒙特島'''（{{lang-en|Belmont Island}}），是[[纽约|紐約市]][[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]所屬的一個人造小島。它長約60米，寬約30米，位於[[羅斯福島_(紐約)|羅斯福島]]前端<ref>{{cite web | title=New York's Treasure Trove of Tiny Islands | website=MetroFocus | date=October 11, 2011 | url=https://www.thirteen.org/metrofocus/2011/10/the-archipelago-of-new-york-city/ | access-date=July 12, 2019 | archive-date=2019-07-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719055605/https://www.thirteen.org/metrofocus/2011/10/the-archipelago-of-new-york-city/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last=Frishberg | first=Hannah | title=Get To Know 34 of New York City's Most Obscure Islands | website=Curbed NY | date=August 26, 2014 | url=https://ny.curbed.com/maps/get-to-know-34-of-new-york-citys-most-obscure-islands | access-date=July 12, 2019 | archive-date=2019-07-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712163554/https://ny.curbed.com/maps/get-to-know-34-of-new-york-citys-most-obscure-islands | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 位置與主權 ==
这个微型人工岛的大小为30x60米，位于罗斯福岛以南的东河中<ref>{{cite news |title=Sand, Surf and Shoobies |first=Jennifer |last=Mascia |url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9A00EEDB1331F936A35754C0A96F9C8B63 |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=July 5, 2009 |accessdate=February 28, 2010 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019221615/https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9A00EEDB1331F936A35754C0A96F9C8B63 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite map |publisher=[[National_Oceanic_and_Atmospheric_Administration|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] |title=Chart 12335 |url=http://www.charts.noaa.gov/OnLineViewer/12335.shtml |date=April 1, 2009 |scale=1 : 10,000 |accessdate=February 28, 2010 |archive-date=2020-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207100236/https://charts.noaa.gov/OnLineViewer/12335.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它的西邊是曼哈顿的第42街的[[联合国总部大楼|联合国总部]]，東邊是[[長島|长岛]][[皇后區|皇后区]]的Gantry Plaza国家公园。它属于曼哈顿管轄，并且是曼哈顿社区第6区（Manhattan Community District 6）的一部分，该区还包括吴丹島以西的Turtle Bay和Murray Hill社区<ref name="NYCPlanning">{{cite web|title=NYC Planning {{!}} Community Profiles|url=https://communityprofiles.planning.nyc.gov/manhattan/6|website=communityprofiles.planning.nyc.gov|publisher=New York City Department of City Planning|accessdate=March 18, 2019|archive-date=2019-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323162103/https://communityprofiles.planning.nyc.gov/manhattan/6|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该岛归纽约州政府所有，目前受到保护，作为包括[[角鸕鶿|角鸕鶿]]在內的鸟类迁徙的棲息所。 从2000年到2011年，角鸕鶿的數量增加了一倍以上<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nps.gov/gate/learn/nature/upload/Elbin-and-Craig-DCCO-2011-Dec-5.pdf|title=Cormorant Population  in the NY Harbor|last=|first=|date=December 5, 2011|website=National Park Service|publisher=New York City Audubon|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181219044257/https://www.nps.gov/gate/learn/nature/upload/Elbin-and-Craig-DCCO-2011-Dec-5.pdf|archive-date=2018-12-19|access-date=December 18, 2018|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
[[File:U_Thant_Island_construction_1906.jpg|thumb]]
1890年代，威廉·施坦威（William Steinway）建造了两条施坦威隧道（Steinway Tunnel），供东河下的火車用来将曼哈顿与他同名的公司镇施坦威村（Steinway Village，位于皇后区）相连。作为该建设项目的一部分，人們将一根竖井挖入称为Man-o'-War  

dReef的出露的花岗岩中。修築隧道产生了多余的垃圾，这些垃圾堆填了礁石并形成了一个小岛。 施坦威在隧道完工之前就去世了，金融家奥古斯特·贝尔蒙特（August Belmont Jr.）在1907年完成了该项目。並以自己名字命名了這個島。1906年，在岛下发生的一起竖井事故中有四名工人死亡<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://cdnc.ucr.edu/?a=d&d=LAH19060117.2.18&e=-------en--20--1--txt-txIN--------1|title=Four Lose Their Lives in Tunnel Disaster|work=Los Angeles Herald|date=17 January 1906|via=California Digital Newspaper Collection|access-date=2018-12-20|archive-date=2018-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221041807/https://cdnc.ucr.edu/?a=d&d=LAH19060117.2.18&e=-------en--20--1--txt-txIN--------1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。直接在岛下通过的隧道現在仍由[[IRT法拉盛線|IRT法拉盛线]]的列车使用，已成为纽约地铁系统的一部分<ref>{{cite journal |last=Rogoff |first=David |year=1960 |url=http://nycsubway.org/wiki/The_Steinway_Tunnels_%281960%29 |title=The Steinway Tunnels |journal=Electric Railroads |issue=29 |access-date=2020-08-22 |archive-date=2019-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210061431/https://www.nycsubway.org/wiki/The_Steinway_Tunnels_(1960) |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1977年，该岛被联合国的一个称为“和平冥想”（Peace Meditation）的组织使用。這個組織由联合国总部的雇员以及曾經的牧师斯里·钦莫伊（Sri Chinmoy）的信徒組成。他们从纽约州租借了该岛，对其表面进行了绿化，并非正式地将其改名为钦莫伊的朋友、前联合国秘书长、缅甸人[[吴丹|吴丹]]。 吴丹岛之名虽然是非正式的，但已成为该岛的俗称<ref>{{cite news |last=Baard |first=Erik |title=Holy Waters |work=[[The_Village_Voice|The Village Voice]] |location=New York |date=June 4, 2002 |url=http://www.villagevoice.com/2002-06-04/news/holy-waters |accessdate=July 12, 2009 |archive-date=2014-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140430102745/http://www.villagevoice.com/2002-06-04/news/holy-waters/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

